{"tid":859030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國波台先係全連登清泉，不服來辯","createTime":"2018-10-12T08:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:34:48.000Z","uid":27939,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c7da0d4eae2486267c029a47538431518e30ed7d","tid":859030,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"講緊係對有色人種既偏見，成見<br />\n<br />\n一般連登仔為左踩低有色人種<br />\n將marvel套黑豹踩到一文不值<br />\n甚至要吹捧外國各大影評網都劣評既Venom<br />\n突顯眾人皆醉我獨醒既高階品味<br />\n<br />\n反觀波台各位手足<br />\n唔理黑貓定白貓，只會支持自己喜歡既球員<br />\n爵連拉車<br />\n摸西先沙勞老鼠<br />\n埃及文明<br />\n史達寧獲加<br />\n數兩數都咁多人係到<br />\n都仲未計d玩具撚<br />\n<br />\n好心d 90後00後就學下野啦<br />\n拉低曬成個討論區既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f7ec5e74d92d48a8298b2644a73548f40a54be","tid":859030,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebff581f55b6186f482ca0bbefc942b016007d72","tid":859030,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"爵連真心高汁"},{"pid":"73e8a83492ee612073865825af461675f14e8b36","tid":859030,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"Pogba@波台：<br />\n<br />\n<em>我好撚憎黑鬼</em>"},{"pid":"cdf7396f75f1c95f91891d7a0967536c98970277","tid":859030,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e8a83492ee612073865825af461675f14e8b36","tid":859030,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"Pogba@波台：<br />\n<br />\n<em>我好撚憎黑鬼</em>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"口是心非啦好明顯<br />\n咪搶口"},{"pid":"fd49bfed66af72dcc6fd5abee82d4863122a7dc0","tid":859030,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebff581f55b6186f482ca0bbefc942b016007d72","tid":859030,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T